<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>[Your Name]</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Aptos', 'Calibri', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #fff;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        header {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: normal;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #000;
        }

        .intro {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .intro a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .intro a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .cv-link {
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .cv-link a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .cv-link a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .paper {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .paper-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #000;
        }

        .paper-title a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .paper-title a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .paper-authors {
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .paper-authors a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .paper-authors a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .paper-abstract {
            text-align: justify;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .paper-presentations {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #555;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .external-link {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .external-link a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .external-link a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .separator {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .work-in-progress {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .wip-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .portrait, .portrait-placeholder {
                width: 150px;
                height: 180px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
            
            .intro {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
                text-align: justify;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>[Your Name]</h1>
        
        <div class="social-links">
            <a href="https://x.com/[your_x_handle]" target="_blank">X</a>
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/[your-linkedin-profile]" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="intro">
            I am [Your Current Position] at <a href="[Institution URL]" target="_blank">[Institution Name]</a>. My research interests are in [your main field] with a specific emphasis on [your specialization]. I am currently interested in [current research focus]. I obtained my PhD in [Field] in [Month Year] from the <a href="[University URL]" target="_blank">[University Name]</a>. During my doctoral studies, I worked as [any relevant positions/internships].
        </div>
        <div class="cv-link">
            Please find here my <a href="files/CV_[YourName].pdf" target="_blank">CV</a>.
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Working Papers</h2>
            
            <div class="paper">
                <div class="paper-title">
                    <a href="files/[paper1_filename].pdf" target="_blank">[Your First Paper Title]: [Subtitle if applicable]</a>
                </div>
                <div class="paper-authors">
                    (with <a href="[coauthor1_url]" target="_blank">[Co-author 1 Name]</a> and <a href="[coauthor2_url]" target="_blank">[Co-author 2 Name]</a>)
                </div>
                <div class="paper-abstract">
                    In this paper, we investigate [brief description of your research question and approach]. We develop and estimate [methodology] using [data description] for the sample [time period]. We conduct [analysis type] to assess [what you're measuring]. Our [analysis type] indicates that [key findings]. However, [important caveat or limitation]. Our [additional analysis] indicates that [additional findings]. Lastly, we find that [final key result].
                </div>
                <div class="paper-presentations">
                    Presented at: [Conference 1] ([Month Year]), [Conference 2] ([Month Year]), [Conference 3], [etc.].
                </div>
                <div class="external-link">
                    <a href="[external_link_if_applicable]" target="_blank">[External Repository/Working Paper Series]</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="paper">
                <div class="paper-title">
                    <a href="files/[paper2_filename].pdf" target="_blank">[Your Second Paper Title]: [Subtitle]</a>
                </div>
                <div class="paper-authors">
                    (with <a href="[coauthor_url]" target="_blank">[Co-author Name]</a> and <a href="[coauthor2_url]" target="_blank">[Co-author 2 Name]</a>)
                </div>
                <div class="paper-abstract">
                    In this paper, we provide new evidence on [research topic] and their [specific focus]. First, we develop [theoretical model] which is solved using [methods]. Through [analysis method], we show that [key theoretical finding]. To validate these findings, we provide [empirical evidence type] from [data source]. Our analysis reveals that [empirical finding 1]. Additionally, and in contrast with results from our theoretical model, we find that [contrasting empirical finding]. Finally, [additional analysis] evidence supports [conclusion].
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <hr class="separator">

        <section class="section work-in-progress">
            <div class="wip-title">Work in progress</div>
            
            <div class="paper">
                <div class="paper-title">
                    <a href="files/[wip_filename].pdf" target="_blank">[Work in Progress Title]</a>
                </div>
                <div class="paper-authors">
                    (with <a href="[coauthor_url]" target="_blank">[Co-author Name]</a>)
                </div>
                <div class="paper-abstract">
                    This work explores [research question] in [context/country/time period]. Our findings suggest that [preliminary findings]. To further investigate these findings, we analyse this relationship through the lens of [theoretical framework]. This analysis contributes to literature by [contribution 1], offering insights into [contribution 2].
                </div>
                <div class="paper-presentations">
                    Presented at: [Conference/Workshop 1] ([Month Year]) and [Conference/Workshop 2] ([format, Month Year]).
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <script>
        // Simple fade-in animation on page load
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            document.body.style.opacity = '0';
            document.body.style.transition = 'opacity 0.5s ease-in';
            
            setTimeout(function() {
                document.body.style.opacity = '1';
            }, 100);
        });

        // Smooth scrolling for any internal links
        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                const target = document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href'));
                if (target) {
                    target.scrollIntoView({
                        behavior: 'smooth',
                        block: 'start'
                    });
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
